main_text: 🥥Simple snack Idea🥥If you are in need of a quick snack that reminds you of summer then this is the snack for you 😌Here’s the recipe :🥥Grab yourself some tinned peaches and slice into quarters🥥mix together 3tbsp of greek yogurt and 2tbsp of coconut milk🥥layer the peaches on a plate and add the coconut yogurt mixture on top🥥for toppings sprinkle with some granoladesiccated coconut and a drizzle of honey for some extra sweetness🥥you could also use crushed cereal or some chopped nuts if you don’t have granola🧡Enjoy!!🧡•••••#healthyfood #healthyrecipes #healthylifestyle #healthyeating #healthybreakfast #healthyliving #healthymeal #healthysnacks #healthysnack #healthysnackideas #healthysnacking #balance #balanceddiet #recipe #recipeoftheday #recipeshare #snacks #snacktime #healthandwellness #aestheticfood #aestheticfoodie #foodie #foodiesofinstagram #discoverunder1k #discoverunder5k #coconut #peach #coconutrecipes #peachrecipes #simplefood
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "lifewithliviana_"  "comment_text": "🥥Simple snack Idea🥥

If you are in need of a quick snack that reminds you of summer then this is the snack for you 😌

Here’s the recipe :
🥥Grab yourself some tinned peaches and slice into quarters
🥥mix together 3tbsp of greek yogurt and 2tbsp of coconut milk
🥥layer the peaches on a plate and add the coconut yogurt mixture on top
🥥for toppings sprinkle with some granola desiccated coconut and a drizzle of honey for some extra sweetness
🥥you could also use crushed cereal or some chopped nuts if you don’t have granola

🧡Enjoy!!🧡
